  <verse number="8" style="v" />But since we are sons of the day, let us be sober. Let us put on the breastplate of faith and love, and, for a helmet, the certainty of future salvation.

  <verse number="9" style="v" />For God did not destine us for wrath, but to obtain salvation through our Lord Jesus Christ.

  <verse number="10" style="v" />It is he who died for us so that, whether we are awake or asleep, we may live together with him.

  <verse number="11" style="v" />Therefore comfort one another and build each other up, just as you are already doing.</para>
